title: Gene Vincent & Eddie Cochran - Rock and Roll Heroes
description:
For collectors only
-------------------

English LP
Rockstar Records RSR-LP 1004

Eddie Cochran & Gene Vincent - Rock 'n' roll heroes 

from english "Saturday Club" radio programme, 1960

Side 1
Say mama - Gene Vincent
- Brian Matthew interviews Gene and reads a request for his next song 
Summertime - Gene Vincent
- Brian Matthew interviews two of Eddie's fans
Somethin' else - Eddie Cochran
- Brian Matthews talks to Eddie who reads a request for his next song
Hallelujah I love her so - Eddie Cochran
- Brian Matthew introduces Gene's next song and Eddie to join 'The Wildcats' 
  on guitar for this number
Wildcat - Gene Vincent
My heart - Gene Vincent

Side 2
- Introduction by Brian Matthew
What'd I say - Eddie Cochran
- Brian Matthew interviews Eddie who introduces his next song
Milk cow blues - Eddie Cochran
Rocky road blues - Gene Vincent
Be bop a lula  - Gene Vincent
- Introduction by Brian Matthew and Eddie announce his next song
Twenty flight rock - Eddie Cochran
